{"tid":2318299,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部發言人趙立堅冀澳洲客觀理性看待中澳合作和「一帶一路」倡議","createTime":"2020-12-09T08:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T08:55:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b1253df427daed00ccc1b7619624d7291793f8bf","tid":2318299,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅就澳洲國會通過《對外關係法案》表示，立法屬於各國內部事務，中方不予評論，希望澳方客觀、理性看待中澳合作和「一帶一路」倡議。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，根據法案，聯邦政府可以阻止各州、地方議會、機構等與外國政府達成協議，例如2018年維多利亞州與中國之間的「一帶一路」協議。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅表示，澳方不要給中澳之間正常的交流合作人為設置障礙，不要搞選擇性、歧視性執法，多做有利於中澳互信和互利的事。他強調，中國和澳洲經貿等領域多年來、來之不易的交流合作成果，符合雙方的共同利益。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564406-20201209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564406-20201209.htm&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUKF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=d1a3ff0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564406-20201209.htm&h=3075e612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564406-20201209.htm</a>"},{"pid":"191e9d5d55b03f8ee372fba418c775e05b83cbe5","tid":2318299,"uid":221650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:49:45.000Z","msg":"成個澳洲得 vic 想玩一戴一露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而州本身又無權做外交層面既野，法庭 ban 都好合理"},{"pid":"8bd5dd4ed0f5080f1a5d24fc8291615eef2178e7","tid":2318299,"uid":66898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"州政府 同國家外交政策有抵觸 緊係睇最大個個話事 咁都好罵<br />\n重要罵個D野全部自己中曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}